description: This one is straight out of a magazine! Spanning 1,421 sq ft, this 2-bed + home office, 2.5-bath stunner is packed with style and substance. The show-stopping kitchen sets the tone w/ a dramatic waterfall island, Thermador appliances, stainless steel hood vent, and seamless flow into the dining area complete with a custom beverage bar and wine fridge. The oversized living room stuns with its generous layout that fits all your furnishings with ease, and direct access to the private back deck—perfect for indoor-outdoor living. Retreat to the king-sized master featuring a spa-like ensuite bath and large closet. The 2nd bedroom is equally spacious, offering its own ensuite with a bathtub. Working from home is effortless in the custom home office, while added perks like in-unit laundry, a 1/2 bath for guests, deeded off-street parking, and basement storage take convenience to the next level. All of this, ideally located on South Boston’s coveted East Side close to nightlife and beaches.
